snippet.title: Small Super Mario Bros.  U -  Release Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD HERE: https://youtu.be/SY608c1phnU (SSMBU2 has all SSMBU levels in world 1)

It's finally here! SSMBU is out.
This is a one world hack made by me, mrbengtsson, from the other team.
Have fun playing!

--Some great discord servers if you want to get started in hacking NSMBU--
Evolution: https://discord.gg/aZAaXVJ
Miyamoto: https://discord.gg/AvFEHpp
